{"title_page": "Altbachisches Archiv", "text_new": "'''{{lang|de|Altbachisches Archiv}}''', also '''{{lang|de|Alt-Bachische Archiv}}''' ('''ABA''', old-Bachian archive), is a collection of 17th-century vocal music, most of which was written by members of the [[Bach family]].\n\n==History==\n[[Johann Ambrosius Bach]], [[Johann Sebastian Bach|Johann Sebastian]]'s father, supposedly started to collect compositions by his relatives. [[Bach's Nekrolog|Johann Sebastian Bach's obituary]] starts with an overview of the composers whose works are contained in the {{lang|de|Altbachisches Archiv}}. [[Carl Philipp Emanuel Bach]], Johann Sebastian's son and co-author of his obituary, retained the collection and gave it its name. After his death the largest part of the collection came, via {{Interlanguage link multi|Georg P\u00f6lchau|de|3=Georg Poelchau|lt=Georg P\u00f6lchau}}, in the possession of the [[Sing-Akademie zu Berlin]]. All nine motets of the Sing-Akademie's part of the ABA collection, including [[BWV&nbsp;1164]], at the time attributed to [[Johann Christoph Bach]], were published in the early 1820s.{{sfn|Melamed|1988|pp=495\u2013498}}\n\nThe manuscripts of two compositions contained in the Sing-Akademie's part of the ABA collection were sold to the Royal Library in Berlin (later renamed as [[Berlin State Library]]): thus [[List of compositions by Johann Sebastian Bach#BNB|BNB]]&nbsp;I/B/11 and BWV&nbsp;1164 were no longer in the Sing-Akademie's archives by the end of the 19th century.{{sfn|Melamed|1988|pp=497\u2013498}} In 1935 [[Max Schneider (music historian)|Max Schneider]], recovering ABA manuscripts scattered in the Sing-Akademie's archive,{{sfn|Melamed|1988|pp=495\u2013496}} published a selection of these compositions, an edition which was reprinted in 1966.<ref name=\"Schneider\">Schneider 1935/1966.</ref> ABA numbers derive from this publication in two volumes.<ref name=\"Schneider\" /> The original manuscripts of the Sing-Akademie's archive went lost during the [[Second World War]],{{sfn|Melamed|1988|p=496}} only to be rediscovered in [[Ukraine]] in 1999, after which they were returned to the Sing-Akademie, which in turn deposited the recovered manuscripts in the Berlin State Library for conservation.<ref>Fischer/Kornemann 2009.</ref><ref>Veit 2007.</ref>\n\n==Compositions==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ Altbachisches Archiv\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | ABA\n! scope=\"col\" | BNB\n! scope=\"col\" | Composer\n! scope=\"col\" | Composition\n! scope=\"col\" | Genre\n! scope=\"col\" | Scoring\n! scope=\"col\" | [[List of compositions by Johann Sebastian Bach#BD|BDW]]\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"101\" | I, 1\n| I/An/11\n| [[Johannes Bach]] {{nobreak|([[Johann Michael Bach]]?)}}\n| ''Sei nun wieder zufrieden''\n| [[motet]] ([[aria]])\n| [[SATB|SSAT+ATTB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8736|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"102\" | I, 2\n| I/B/43\n| [[Johannes Bach]] {{nobreak|([[Johann Michael Bach]]?)}}\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Unser Leben ist ein Schatten|scores|3=Unser Leben ist ein Schatten (Bach, Johann)|lt=Unser Leben ist ein Schatten}}''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SSATTB+ATB]]\n| {{BD0|8740|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"103\" | I, 3\n| I/An/12\n| [[Johannes Bach]]\n| ''Weint nicht um meinen Tod''\n| [[motet]] ([[aria]])\n| [[SATB]]\n| {{BD0|8741|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"104\" | I, 4\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]?\n| ''Unser Leben w\u00e4hret siebenzig Jahr''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATT]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8743|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"105\" | I, 5\n| I/B/39\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Das Blut Jesu Christi|scores|3=Das Blut Jesu Christi (Bach, Johann Michael)|lt=Das Blut Jesu Christi}}''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATTB]] [[Cornett|Cnt]] 3[[Trombone|Tbn]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8744|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"106\" | I, 6\n| I/B/40\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Herr, wenn ich nur dich habe|scores|3=Herr, wenn ich nur dich habe (Bach, Johann Michael)|lt=Herr, wenn ich nur dich habe}}'' ({{nobreak|14 November 1690}})\n| [[Geistliches Konzert]] (funeral&nbsp;[[motet]])\n| [[SATB|SATTB]]\n| {{BD0|8745|0}}\n|- id=\"ABA I, 7\"\n| data-sort-value=\"107\" | I, 7\n| I/B/41\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Ich wei\u00df, dass mein Erl\u00f6ser lebt (J. M. Bach)|scores|3=Ich weiss dass mein Erl\u00f6ser lebt (Bach, Johann Michael)|lt=Ich wei\u00df, dass mein Erl\u00f6ser lebt}}''\n| {{nobreak|[[Geistliches Konzert]]}}\n| [[SATB|SATTB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8748|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"108\" | I, 8\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Sei lieber Tag willkommen|scores|3=Sei, lieber Tag, willkommen (Bach, Johann Michael)|lt=Sei lieber Tag willkommen}}''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SSATTB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8749|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"109\" | I, 9\n| I/B/42\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Nun hab' ich \u00fcberwunden|scores|3=Nun hab Ich \u00fcberwunden (Bach, Johann Michael)|lt=Nun hab' ich \u00fcberwunden}}''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATB+SATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8750|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"110\" | I, 10\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Halt, was du hast''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATB+ATTB]]&nbsp;[[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8864|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"111\" | I, 11\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|F\u00fcrchtet euch nicht|scores|3=F\u00fcrchtet euch nicht (Bach, Johann Michael)|lt=F\u00fcrchtet euch nicht}}''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATB+SATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8752|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"112\" | I, 12\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Herr, du l\u00e4ssest mich erfahren''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATB+ATTB]]&nbsp;[[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8756|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"113\" | I, 13\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{nobreak|Dem Menschen ist gesetzt einmal zu sterben}}''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATB+ATTB]]&nbsp;[[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8757|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"114\" | I, 14\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Herr, ich warte auf dein Heil''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SATB+SATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8758|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"115\" | I, 15\n| I/An/10\n| [[Adam Drese]] (not [[Heinrich&nbsp;Bach]])\n| ''Nun ist alles \u00fcberwunden''\n| [[motet]] ([[aria]])\n| [[SATB]]\n| {{BD0|9090|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"116\" | I, 16\n| I/B/12\n| [[Johann Christoph Bach]]\n| ''Es ist nun aus mit meinem Leben''\n| [[motet]] ([[aria]])\n| [[SATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8760|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"117\" | I, 17\n| I/B/16\n| [[Johann Christoph Bach]]\n| ''Mit Weinen hebt sichs an''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8762|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"118\" | I, 18\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Christoph Bach]]\n| ''Der Mensch, vom Weibe geboren''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SSATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8763|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"119\" | I, 19\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Christoph Bach]]\n| ''Sei getreu bis in den Tod''\n| [[motet]]\n| [[SATB|SSATB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8764|0}}\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"120\" | I, 20\n| I/B/10\n| [[Johann Christoph Bach]]\n| ''Der Gerechte, ob er gleich zu zeitlich stirbt'' (1675)\n| [[motet]] (funeral)\n| [[SATB|SATTB]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8850|0}}\n|- id=\"Ich danke dir, Gott, ABA II, 1\"\n| data-sort-value=\"201\" | II, 1\n| \u2014\n| [[Heinrich Bach]]\n| ''Ich danke dir, Gott''\n| [[Church cantata#17th Sunday after Trinity (Trinity XVII)|church cantata (Trinity&nbsp;XVII)]]\n| [[SATB|SSATB+SSATB]] 2[[Violin|Vl]] 2[[Viola|Va]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8787|0}}\n|- id=\"Siehe, wie fein und lieblich ist, ABA II, 2\"\n| data-sort-value=\"202\" | II, 2\n| data-sort-value=\"I/B/03\" | I/B/3\n| [[Georg Christoph Bach]]\n| ''Siehe, wie fein und lieblich ist'' ({{nobreak|6 September 1689}}; after [[Psalm 133|Ps.&nbsp;133]])\n| [[Church cantata#Birthday|church cantata / vocal concerto (birthday)]]\n| [[SATB|ttb]] [[Violin|Vl]] 3[[Viola da gamba|Vdg]] [[Violone|Vne]] [[Organ (music)|Org]]\n| {{BD0|8789|0}}\n|- id=\"Es ist ein gro\u00dfer Gewinn, ABA II, 3\"\n| data-sort-value=\"203\" | II, 3\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Es ist ein gro\u00dfer Gewinn''\n| [[Church cantata#Occasion not known or uncertain|church cantata (unknown&nbsp;occ.)]]\n| [[SATB|s]] [[Violino piccolo|Vlp]] 3[[Violin|Vl]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8792|0}}\n|- id=\"Ach, wie sehnlich wart' ich der Zeit, ABA II, 4\"\n| data-sort-value=\"204\" | II, 4\n| I/B/37\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Ach, wie sehnlich wart' ich der Zeit''\n| [[Church cantata#Occasion not known or uncertain|church cantata (unknown&nbsp;occ.)]]\n| [[SATB|s]] 5[[String instrument|Str]] [[Organ (music)|Org]]\n| {{BD0|8794|0}}\n|- id=\"Auf, lasst uns den Herren loben, ABA II, 5\"\n| data-sort-value=\"205\" | II, 5\n| I/B/38\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Auf, lasst uns den Herren loben|scores|3=Auf, la\u00dft uns den Herren loben (Bach, Johann Michael)}}''\n| [[Church cantata#Occasion not known or uncertain|church cantata / Aria (unknown&nbsp;occ.)]]\n| [[SATB|a]] 4[[String instrument|Str]] [[basso continuo|Bc]] ([[Violone|Vne]], [[Organ (music)|Org]])\n| {{BD0|8796|0}}\n|- id=\"Liebster Jesu, h\u00f6r mein Flehen, ABA II, 6\"\n| data-sort-value=\"206\" | II, 6\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Liebster Jesu, h\u00f6r mein Flehen''\n| [[Church cantata#Second Sunday of Lent (Reminiscere)|church cantata (Reminiscere)]]\n| [[SATB|SATTB]] 2[[Violin|Vl]] 2[[Viola|Va]] [[basso continuo|Bc]]\n| {{BD0|8798|0}}\n|- id=\"Ach bleib bei uns, Herr Jesu Christ, ABA II, 7\"\n| data-sort-value=\"207\" | II, 7\n| \u2014\n| [[Johann Michael Bach]]\n| ''Ach bleib bei uns, Herr Jesu Christ''\n| [[Church cantata#Occasion not known or uncertain|church cantata (unknown&nbsp;occ.)]]\n| [[SATB]] 2[[Violin|Vl]] 3[[Viola|Va]] [[basso c