h (footballer)|Harpal Singh]] - {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]], 7 November 2002<ref name=\"november\" />\n* {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Shane Cansdell-Sherriff]] - {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Rochdale A.F.C.|Rochdale]], 8 November 2002<ref name=\"november\" />\n* {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Jamie McMaster]] - {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Coventry City F.C.|Coventry City]], 19 November 2002<ref name=\"november\" />\n* {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Craig Stiens]] - {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Swansea City A.F.C.|Swansea City]], 13 December 2002<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/2903925.stm | work=BBC News | title=Swansea escape with reprimand | date=31 March 2003}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Olivier Dacourt]] - {{flagicon|ITA}} [[A.S. Roma|Roma]], 8 January 2003<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2003/jan/09/newsstory.sport3 | work=The Guardian | title=Dacourt joins Leeds exodus | date=9 January 2003}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Frazer Richardson]] - {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Stoke City F.C.|Stoke City]], 10 January 2003<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/2733919.stm | work=BBC News | title=Richardson loan extended | date=6 February 2003}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Danny Milosevic]] - {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Crewe Alexandra F.C.|Crewe Alexandra]], 20 January 2003<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/2678005.stm | work=BBC News | title=Milosevic goes to Crewe | date=20 January 2003}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tom Newey]] - {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Darlington F.C.|Darlington]], 29 March 2003<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2820571.stm | work=BBC News | title=Transfers - March 2003 | date=14 April 2003}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|32em}}\n\n{{Leeds United A.F.C. seasons}}\n{{2002\u201303 in English football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2002-03 Leeds United A.F.C. season}}\n[[Category:2002\u201303 FA Premier League by team|Leeds United]]